title: Brief Update - Sorry about Sunday!
description: I was unable to do the reading video on Sunday, but I will make up for it! Thanks to everyone for your support and getting me over the 1k mark. I attribute most of this to the recent interviews with Paul and Jonathan. I am grateful to be included in what I believe to be a critically important discussion. Thanks so much to John Vervaeke for giving us the language...and the problem...The Meaning Crisis
